data.description: First thing you will notice driving up to this home is that it is in a cul-de-sac.  Then you will love the pond that is in the front yard that is fully functioning.  Heading into the home you will see the spacious family room and head around the corner to the dining room and beautiful kitchen w/ newer appliances.  Heading upstairs you have 3 well-sized bedrooms and one bathroom with some nice upgrades aswell.  Basement is perfect for hanging out and having fun.  Then you add the 4th bedroom in the basement and you have a nice sized home.  But wait!  Have you seen the backyard?  Have you seen the views of Pikes Peak?  Have you noticed there is open space behind the house with amazing trails to walk!!!
